data.description: Come see this 13-acre estate in the highly desirable area of Jefferson, this gorgeous 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of rustic charm and modern amenities. Whether you are just looking for peace and quiet or to raise some cattle, this is it!  As you approach the property, the scenic driveway welcomes you to a beautiful front yard that sets the stage for this stunning home. Inside, the house features a spacious plan with a cozy living room, perfect for family gatherings. The kitchen is a chef’s delight, boasting modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and gorgeous countertops.  The home’s bedrooms are generously sized, each offering comfortable living quarters with plenty of natural light. The master suite includes a private bathroom with large walk in shower. Step outside to discover a backyard oasis designed for relaxation and entertainment. The highlight is the pristine in-ground swimming pool, surrounded by a spacious patio area ideal for summer barbecues and pool parties. The property also includes multiple pole barns and outbuildings, offering abundant space for storage, workshops, or potentially converting into guest accommodations. Additional features of this property include: A large laundry room with extra storage. An attached two-car garage, providing convenience and security. Energy-efficient windows that fill the home with natural light while keeping utility costs low. This home is not just a dwelling but a lifestyle, providing endless opportunities for outdoor activities and hobbies. Whether you're tending to your garden, exploring the wooded acreage, or simply enjoying the tranquility of your private estate, this property caters to all. Located in the peaceful yet accessible area of Jefferson, you are just minutes away from local schools, shopping, dining, and more, combining the best of country living with the conveniences of city amenities. Don’t miss out on the chance to own this magnificent country home. Whether you're looking for a family home or a peaceful retreat, this property promises to be a place where cherished memories are made. Schedule your private viewing today and start living the dream!
